{"name":"研究型论文","slug":"研究型论文","count":2,"postlist":[{"title":"Generative Agents: Interactive Simulacra of Human Behavior","uid":"b8952af59fed72e672d831cb050186be","slug":"Generative-Agents-Interactive-Simulacra-of-Human-Behavior","date":"2023-11-16T16:12:01.000Z","updated":"2023-11-22T16:48:17.375Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Generative-Agents-Interactive-Simulacra-of-Human-Behavior.json","keywords":"Agent; blog; LLM; GPT","cover":[],"text":"背景：一个可信赖的智能体可以增强交互式应用的效果，比如沉浸式环境和交互式交流的工具等。目的：引入了通用智能体去模拟人类社会的交互行为，同时为了确保生成式智能体的可靠性，该文章描述了智能体的框架，并做出了可信任的评价结果。结论：该智能体框架对agent行为的可信性有重要贡献，通过融合LLM和agent，本文引入了架构和交互模式，以实现对人类行为的可信的智能体模拟。...","permalink":"/post/Generative-Agents-Interactive-Simulacra-of-Human-Behavior","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"paper","slug":"paper","count":2,"path":"api/tags/paper.json"},{"name":"AIagent","slug":"AIagent","count":3,"path":"api/tags/AIagent.json"},{"name":"研究型论文","slug":"研究型论文","count":2,"path":"api/tags/研究型论文.json"}],"author":{"name":"Jason","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/man.jpg","link":"/","description":"A man who are student for AI.","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/qingqiyangqidanqi","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/sheng-huo-74-25","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_45833373?type=blog","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},{"title":"MetaGPT: Meta Programming for A Multi-Agent","uid":"32bfaef6000bd85355288e04621c5f1d","slug":"MetaGPT-Meta-Programming-for-A-Multi-Agent","date":"2023-11-14T14:59:59.000Z","updated":"2023-11-22T16:40:58.391Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/MetaGPT-Meta-Programming-for-A-Multi-Agent.json","keywords":"Agent; blog; LLM; GPT","cover":[],"text":"背景：最近，通过使用大型语言模型( LLMs )驱动的多自主体，在自动化任务解决方面取得了显著的进展。然而，现有的工作主要集中在简单任务上，缺乏对复杂任务的探索和研究，主要原因是幻觉问题。当多个智能体相互作用时，这种幻觉会被无限放大，从而导致在处理复杂问题时失败。目的：引入了MetaGPT,将SOP工作流程引入，同时为多代理分配了不同的角色，建立了一种解决复杂问题的框架。结论：开发了metaGPT，同时，本项目突出了将人类领域知识纳入多智能体的潜力，从而为应对复杂的现实世界挑战开辟了新的途径。...","permalink":"/post/MetaGPT-Meta-Programming-for-A-Multi-Agent","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.2k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"paper","slug":"paper","count":2,"path":"api/tags/paper.json"},{"name":"AIagent","slug":"AIagent","count":3,"path":"api/tags/AIagent.json"},{"name":"研究型论文","slug":"研究型论文","count":2,"path":"api/tags/研究型论文.json"}],"author":{"name":"Jason","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/man.jpg","link":"/","description":"A man who are student for AI.","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/qingqiyangqidanqi","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/sheng-huo-74-25","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_45833373?type=blog","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true}]}